{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Complain about a legal adviser"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/complain-about-legal-adviser.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/complain-about-legal-adviser"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"1936","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Follow your legal adviser's complaints procedure or contact the Legal Ombudsman.","updated_at":"2012-10-02T12:12:28+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Follow your legal adviser\u2019s complaints procedure or contact the Legal Ombudsman.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Ask your legal adviser for a copy of their complaints procedure. This should tell you how to complain and how they will deal with it.</p>\n\n<p>If your legal adviser doesn&rsquo;t respond to your complaint in 8 weeks or if you&rsquo;re unhappy with their response, you can complain to the Legal Ombudsman.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Legal Ombudsman helpline</strong><br />\n0300 555 0333<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legalombudsman.org.uk/\" title=\"Legal Ombudsman website\" rel=\"external\">Legal Ombudsman website</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Or you can write to the Legal Ombudsman:</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nLegal Ombudsman\n<br />PO Box 6806  \n<br />Wolverhampton  \n<br />WV1 9WJ\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Reporting crimes and getting compensation","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/justice%2Freporting-crimes-compensation.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Including criminal injuries compensation and reporting suspected crimes","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=justice%2Freporting-crimes-compensation","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/justice/reporting-crimes-compensation"},"parent":{"title":"Crime, justice and the law","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/justice.j